    content: "Sabine Gerdon is a Business Development Manager for Data Sharing and Innovation based in Berlin. She supports AWS customers and partners in implementing data space projects with a focus on how to generate insights and value from data. Previously she advised the UK Government on data policies and led projects on AI in the public sector as Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning Fellow at the World Economic Forum in San Francisco.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sabinegerdon/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
