    content: "Marc Ribalta is a researcher in Eurecat’s Applied Artificial Intelligence unit. With a Computer Engineering degree from Universitat de Lleida (UdL) and a master’s degree in Big Data, he is pursuing a thesis on Predictive Maintenance for urban water management. Currently, he is actively involved in Machine Learning projects focused on Anomaly Detection, Predictive Maintenance, and Virtual Sensors for the entire water cycle.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/marc-ribalta-gene-240a2b140/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
