    content: "Shuhei found his passion for solving regional issues and creating sustainable businesses through the use of technology and joined NEC to help solve regional issues. He is currently engaged in community activities to promote FIWARE and to form an industry-government-academia ecosystem for the social implementation of smart cities in Japan. In May 2022, he and his team from NEC established iHub Base in Tokyo as the first FIWARE iHub in the Asia Pacific region, and he leads iHub Base as General Community Manager.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/shuhei-sasano-79637a219/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
