    content: "Judith Schultze has been working on Smart City topics at EDAG for almost three years. In Business Development and Sales Smart City, she focuses on the creation of Smart City solutions, to create added value for the citizens. She also sees Smart City as a collaborative effort and is therefore open to exchange and cooperation. This is the only way to master the challenges of tomorrow.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/judith-schultze-4244641b2/", twitter: "https://twitter.com/SchultzeJudith", domain: "", location: "",
